javadoc:
A base implementation for creating an 'About' menu action callback. This is executed when the user presses the Dock's 'Ghidra->About' menu action.

Simply constructing this class will register it.

See com.apple.eawt.Application.setAboutHandler(AboutHandler) com.apple.eawt.AboutHandler.handleAbout(AboutEvent)
